        "subject": "LU-10214 lnet: Add support for gateway range",
        "message": "LU-10214 lnet: Add support for gateway range\n\nCurrently both lctl and lnetctl command does not\nsupport range for gateway parameter while adding routes.\n\nlnet_routes.conf file specifies example to add routes\nusing range for gateway parameter but the feature doesnt\nexist. Adding the feature with this patch for both lctl\nand lnetctl command to allow ranges for gateway\nparameter while adding routes.\n\nChange-Id: I44c968beea0de5f865363164f7d9ff068c5827d9\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nSigned-off-by: Sonia Sharma <sonia.sharma@intel.com>\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
  },
